## Train Herding with Summon Creature(Endless)
## Make sure you have enough summ cre. spell regents in backpack.
## Leave the character on calm area and play script.

if followers < 1
    cast 'Summ. Creature'
    wait 5000
endif

while followers > 0
    say '[focusaggression'
    waitfortarget
    target closest 'friendly'
    wait 2500 
endwhile
loop